<h1>About the UCI Fund</h1>

<div class="text">
  <p>The UCI Fund provides the university with the flexibility to support emerging needs and opportunities on campus. At a time when less than 10 percent of UCI&#8217;s budget comes from the state, your gift of any size is not only a vote of confidence in UCI&#8217;s great work but also an investment in the people and projects touched by Anteaters everywhere.</p>
<br/>
<h3>Why give?</h3>
<p>When you give to the UCI Fund, you are making a significant and immediate impact on the university. Your gift to the UCI Fund helps support one of these three areas across campus.</p>
<br/>
<div id="accordion">
<h2>Student Support</h2>
<div>
<p>UCI is committed to providing a world-class education that is both accessible and affordable for our nation&#8217;s most talented students.</p>
<ul>
<li>Gifts to the UCI Fund provide scholarships and opportunities to deserving Anteaters.</li>
</ul>
<table border="0" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%;" summary="Tuition Assistance">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td align="left" valign="middle" width="20%"><img alt="Alexandra Jimenez" height="100" src="http://give.uci.edu/UCIFund/img/About-Alexandra-Jimenez.png" width="100"/></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle" width="80%"><span style="color: #0064a4; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic;">"I have so many ambitions for the future; and, thanks to generous scholarship support, they are within reach. Coming from a low-income family, I am grateful to all those who have donated so that I could achieve my dream of attending a four-year university like UC Irvine."<br/><br/>Alexandra J., Anthropology Major </span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<br/>
<h2>Faculty Excellence</h2>
<div>
<p>UCI faculty members not only prepare, challenge and inspire our students but also forge new ideas and discoveries that will change the world.</p>
<ul>
<li>Gifts to the UCI Fund support faculty recruitment and supply the resources they need to advance their disciplines and shape the minds of our future leaders.</li>
</ul>
<table border="0" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%;" summary="Faculty Support">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td align="left" valign="middle" width="20%"><img alt="Ryan Davis" height="100" src="http://give.uci.edu/UCIFund/img/About-Ryan-Davis.png" width="100"/></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle" width="80%"><span style="color: #0064a4; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic;">"I came to UC Irvine to study under the greatest faculty in the world. I really credit Dr. Shi for helping me fulfill my passion and giving me the opportunity to assist with cancer research."<br/><br/>Ryan D., Biological Science Major </span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<br/>
<h2>Campus Resources</h2>
<div>
<p>Campus organizations, state-of-the-art technology and personalized mentoring add up to create a UCI experience that is truly second to none.</p>
<ul>
<li>Gifts to the UCI Fund elevate and enrich campus life at one of our nation&#8217;s premier public research universities.</li>
</ul>
<table border="0" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%;" summary="Academic Resources">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td align="left" valign="middle" width="20%"><img alt="Fernando Eleazar Monjaras" height="100" src="http://give.uci.edu/UCIFund/img/About-Fernando-Eleazar-Monjaras.png" width="100"/></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle" width="80%"><span style="color: #0064a4; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic;">"Organizations such as Math Club, Campus Representatives and the Education Abroad Program have aided me in my speaking skills and my ability to gather thoughts together and communicate them clearly."<br/> <br/> Fernando M., Humanities Major</span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
